    "guide-gems-intro": "Each cut gem grants its primary buff when socketed and worn. Baguette gems add a small random secondary on top.",
    "guide-gems-note-negative": "Note: negative values are beneficial for hungerrate / armorDurabilityLoss / animalSeekingRange.",
    "guide-gems-secondary-range": "Secondary value range:",

    "guide-cut-round-title": "Round",
    "guide-cut-round-desc": "Primary stat only. After FULL processing on the jewel grinder this gives the highest main-stat value of any cut. Best long-term choice.",
    "guide-cut-baguette-title": "Baguette",
    "guide-cut-baguette-desc": "Primary stat + a small random secondary buff from a fixed pool for that stat. Trades some main-stat power for a bonus second effect.",
    "guide-cut-pear-title": "Pear",
    "guide-cut-pear-desc": "Primary stat only, but the gem starts much stronger BEFORE grinding. If both gems are fully ground, Round overtakes it. Good for un-ground gems.",

